flowchart TD
    App[Application] --> CheckCache{Cache Hit?}
    CheckCache -->|Yes| ReturnCached[Return cached data]
    CheckCache -->|No| QueryDB[Query database]
    QueryDB --> StoreCache[Store result in cache\nwith TTL]
    StoreCache --> ReturnFresh[Return fresh data]
    ReturnCached --> Client[Client receives data]
    ReturnFresh --> Client

    WriteApp[Application write] --> UpdateDB[(Update database)]
    UpdateDB --> InvalidateKey[Invalidate cache key]
    InvalidateKey --> NextRead[Next read will miss\nand reload from DB]
